1. Overview

   This module produces and sends messages to a Kafka server.

2. Dependencies

   2.1. Kamailio Modules
   2.2. External Libraries or Applications
   2.3. Parameters

        2.3.1. brokers (string)
        2.3.2. configuration (string)
        2.3.3. topic (string)

